---
title: Cheesy Stuffed Chicken Thigh and Sweet Potato Mash with Crunchy Spring Salad
description: Stuffing chicken breast with anything adds a special je-ne-sais-quoi to meals on any night of the week. This cheese-stuffed chicken is just that! Paired with a bright salad and creamy sweet potato mash, it's a winner!
